modules.description: This module implements Git packfile verification, delta resolution, and index generation for low-level object storage. It processes streams of Git objects using Lwt for asynchronous I/O, supporting operations like applying deltas, building packfiles with optional compression, and validating entries against a configuration. Key data structures include `Carton_lwt.config`, `Cartonnage.Entry.t`, and `Cartonnage.Target.t`, with concrete use in reconstructing and verifying Git repositories from raw pack data.
